The idea of a stick of butter turned me off although I could tell from the ingredients list how delicious the finished spread might be. So I substituted the butter for Fage 0% fat Greek Yogurt. The consistancy will be softer than the original recipe but just as tasty with less the fat and calories! I also omitted the salt but used salted roasted pistachios.

